{"type":"HOSTEL","name":"The Surf House","nameEN":"The Surf House","isActive":true,"isNew":false,"description":"The Surf House is a premium and affordable accommodation and roof top bar located100 metres from the Main Beach in Byron Bays town centre.\r\n\r\nThe properties quality private ensuite rooms and unique shared rooms make it a perfect choice for couples, friends or solo travelers looking for a Byron getaway. Together with a prime rooftop bar, the best eateries at your doorstep, and the beach mere minutes away, this accommodation is an ideal base for a coastal escape. \r\n\r\nAccommodation and Bar\r\nHaving recently undergone a major refurbishment, rooms boast a beach-chic design that set the scene for your relaxed, sun-soaked holiday ahead.\r\n\r\nPrivate rooms come with the option of an ensuite, TV, bath towels and your own balcony to enjoy a sundowner. If you are coming to Byron with friends or as a solo traveller, then our spacious shared rooms are a top option, with individual secure storage and linens provided.\r\n\r\nSitting atop the property, is our rooftop bar. This open-air area is complete with, artisan rugs and textiles, coastal-style umbrellas, and trinkets sourced from travels around the world. It is the perfect place to take in a balmy evening with friends, over local Byron Bay brews and freshly made pizzas.\r\n\r\nLocation\r\nRest comfortably knowing we are based in the centre of the very best that Byron has to offer. If you are coming for the surf and sea, its a quick 100m walk to the Main Beach and free surfboards are available to all guests. If its Byrons food and bar scene that interests you, our doors are moments away from the likes of Bayleaf Cafe, Miss Margarita, The Balcony and Combi. Our prime location makes this one of the best affordable accommodation options in Byron Bay.\r\n\r\nUndercover parking is available for guests against a little charge of $10 per day. Providing the freedom for those arriving by car to enjoy day trips to th